sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Create as CreateDogScreen
  participant Zod as Zod
  participant Status as StatusMessage
  User->>Create: fill form
  User->>Create: tap Save
  Create->>Zod: validate(dogFormSchema)
  Zod-->>Create: success/fail
  alt validation fails
    Create-->>User: inline errors
  else success
    Create-->>Status: show inline success message
    Status-->>User: visible confirmation (no persistence)
  end
